def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    b = [int(x) for x in input().split()]

    a_win = 0
    b_win = 0

    for i in range(3):
        a_win += min(a[i], b[(i+1)%3])
        b_win += min(a[(i+1)%3], b[i])

    print(a_win, a_win+n-b_win)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()

def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    b = list(map(int, input().split()))

    a.sort()
    b.sort()

    min_wins = 0
    max_wins = 0

    for i in range(3):
        min_wins += min(a[i], b[2-i])
        max_wins += max(a[i], b[2-i])

    print(min_wins, max_wins)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()

def main():
    n = int(input())
    a1, a2, a3 = map(int, input().split())
    b1, b2, b3 = map(int, input().split())
    a = [a1, a2, a3]
    b = [b1, b2, b3]
    a.sort()
    b.sort()
    if a[0] > b[1]:
        print(b[1], n-a[0])
    else:
        print(a[0], n-b[1])

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
